description.p:
The system as described herein provides a score that Considers—Anatomical/genetic/Physiological and other factors as described above and gives a score to each normal organ—for the risk it may stand in long and short term. To be specific, the system generates and gives overall cumulative risk score.
For disease recurrence (distribution of dose and other factors that may confer resistance to tumor);
Adverse reaction score—for cumulative side effects on all normal tissues—long and short term;
Recovery probability score—for normal tissues/Organs; and/or
Gives permutations and combinations—to help choose best treatment plan
